message:
Shortly after 3AM, the Shia militias in Iraq accepted responsibility for launching a UAV towards a target in Eilat.

Shortly after four in the morning, the IDF spokesperson reported on the successful interception of a target that came from the east and did not penetrate Israeli territory.
event_breakdown: Shia militias in Iraq accept responsibility for launching a UAV towards a target in Eilat.

message:
IDF activity in the Nur Shams refugee camp in Tulkarm

The Palestinians report extensive IDF activity since the night hours until now in the Nur Shams camp.

According to the attached documents, powerful explosive charges were fired at IDF bulldozers that were engaged in uncovering terrorist infrastructures.

The moment of the explosion of one of the charges was recorded on video by the Palestinians.
event_breakdown: IDF activity in the Nur Shams refugee camp in Tulkarm: The Palestinians reported extensive IDF activity since the night hours until now.

message:
Syrian sources: An Israeli drone attacked a vehicle in Syrian territory

Syrian media reports that an Israeli drone recently attacked a vehicle on the Damascus road in Beirut, in Syrian territory, near the Zabora checkpoint.
According to these sources, there are fatalities.
event_breakdown: Israeli drone attack near Zabora checkpoint on Damascus road in Beirut

message: Sa'ad Mosque in Tel al-Sultan in West Rafah after it was attacked by the IDF, according to the Palestinians.
event_breakdown: The Sa'ad Mosque in Tel al-Sultan, located in West Rafah in the Gaza Strip, was attacked on Friday by the Israeli Defense Forces (IDF). The IDF has not commented on the incident. The attack on the mosque comes as tensions have been rising between Israel and the Palestinians in the Gaza Strip.

message:
Hamas Information Bureau:

The occupation is trying to implement its plans to evacuate Gaza City, in order to "gain security", according to them. They calls on the residents of Gaza to leave the city and even forces them to do so by force.

The occupation is trying to turn Gaza City into an unlivable area in order to empty it of its residents and send them south.

The occupation publishes misleading evacuation maps that direct the residents to "safe areas" (but these are not safe according to Hamas - AA).
event_breakdown: The target event is an armed conflict in the Gaza Strip between Palestinian factions and Israeli forces. The event is ongoing and has been reported in news outlets such as Al Jazeera, Reuters, and Haaretz.

message: Gaza sources report that dozens of families who evacuated from Gaza City arrived in Nuseirat in the center of the Gaza Strip and crossed the Netzerim corridor towards the south late last night.
event_breakdown: Gaza sources report that dozens of families who evacuated from Gaza City arrived in Nuseirat in the center of the Gaza Strip and crossed the Netzerim corridor towards the south late last night.
